---
title: Creamy Dreamy Steak & Mushroom Cavatappi with Scallions & Parmesan
description: If you’re mad for mushrooms, a fan of fungi, or crazy for creminis, this pasta will treat you right. After all ’shrooms are the flavor backbone of this recipe, bringing all those deep, earthy flavors that you know and love. We’ve added springy cavatappi, a dreamy garlic herb sauce, and a sprinkling of Parm. Get ready for this umami bomb to make waves at your dinner table.
